_sText:
Basic JailBreak map: ba_jail_panama (Prefinal Release)

# Actual content:
- Soccer stadium(desert style)
- Swimming Pool
- Armory (M3, AK47, M4A1, M249, DEAGLE)
- 14 T Spawns / 10 CT Spawns
- Cage (with boxes)
- Medic (Heals 27hp/sec)
- Observatory (With AWP)


# Secret weapons:
- AWP: Near the Door on the side, find the thin walls to jump on them and finally get up next to the buildings, an AWP with 10/20 ammo is waiting you on a corner :)
- DEAGLE: Search between two boxes of the cage, there is a deagle with 7/35 ammo.
- AK47: Crouch, and in one of the four walls of the pool there is a little wall you can walk through, there is an AK47 with 30/120 ammo, you can stay in the secret room, because you see what is happening outside :D
- SMOKEGRENADE, FLASHBANG, HEGRENADE: In various jails.
